  78:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      (#) Configure Pipe parameters, destination (one or two) and Capture Mode (Snapshot or Continuo
  79:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          the capture request using one from the following functions:
  80:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_Start() or HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_DoubleBufferStart().
  81:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
  82:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          Configure DCMIPP_PIPE1, destination addresses (Y and UV addresses) and Capture Mode (Snaps
