  87:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          and enable the capture request for full-planar buffer using one from the following functio
  88:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_FullPlanarStart() or HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_FullPlanarDoubleBufferStart().
  89:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
  90:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****     (##) Serial Mode
  91:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      (#) Configure Pipe parameter, Virtual Channel, destination (one or two) and Capture Mode (Snap
  92:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          and enable the capture request using the following functions:
  93:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_PIPE_Start() or HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_PIPE_DoubleBufferStart().
  94:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
  95:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          Configure DCMIPP_PIPE1, Virtual Channel, destination addresses (Y and UV addresses) and Ca
  96:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         (Snapshot or Continuous) and enable the capture request for Semi-planar buffer using
  97:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          the following functions:
  98:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_PIPE_SemiPlanarStart() or HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_PIPE_SemiPlanarDoubleBufferStart()
  99:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 100:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          Configure DCMIPP_PIPE1, Virtual Channel, destination addresses (Y, U and V addresses) and 
 101:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         (Snapshot or Continuous) and enable the capture request for Semi-planar buffer
 102:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          using the following functions:
 103:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_PIPE_FullPlanarStart() or HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_PIPE_FullPlanarDoubleBufferStart()
 104:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 105:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      (#) Use HAL_DCMIPP_IRQHandler() called under DCMIPP_IRQHandler() interrupt subroutine.
 106:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      (#) At the end of frame capture request HAL_DCMIPP_IRQHandler() function is executed and user 
 107:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          add his own function by customization of function pointer PipeFrameEventCallback (member
 108:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          of DCMIPP handle structure).
 109:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 110:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****    (#) Use HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_IRQHandler() called under CSI_IRQHandler() interrupt subroutine.
 111:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****    (#) At the start or the end of frame capture HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_IRQHandler() function is executed an
 112:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****        add his own function by customization of function pointer StartOfFrameEventCallback or EndOf
 113:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 114:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****     (#) In case of common error, the HAL_DCMIPP_IRQHandler() function calls the callback
 115:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          ErrorCallback, in case of Pipe error the HAL_DCMIPP_IRQHandler() function calls the callba
 116:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****      and in case of CSI Line error the HAL_DCMIPP_CSI_IRQHandler() function calls the callback
 117:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****          LineErrorCallback.
 118:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 119:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****     (#) The Pipe capture can be suspended and resumed using the following functions
 120:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_Suspend() and HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_Resume().
 121:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 122:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****     (#) For Snapshot Mode the capture can be re-enabled using the HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_EnableCapture();
 123:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 124:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****     (#) Optionally, Program the required configuration through the following parameters:
 125:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         Client, MemoryPageSize, Traffic, MaxOutstandingTransactions, DPREGStart, DPREGEnd
 126:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         and WLRURatio using HAL_DCMIPP_SetIPPlugConfig().
 127:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 128:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****     (#) Optionally, configure and Enable the CROP feature to select a rectangular
 129:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         window from the received image using HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_SetCropConfig()
 130:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         and HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_EnableCrop() functions.
 131:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 132:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****     (#) Optionally, configure and Enable the line and bytes decimation features
 133:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         using the following functions HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_SetLinesDecimationConfig and
 134:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_SetBytesDecimationConfig.
 135:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 136:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****     (#) Optionally, configure and enable the line event using the function HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_EnableLi
 137:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 138:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****     (#) Optionally, configure and enable the Limit event using the function HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_EnableL
 139:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
