 140:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****     (#) If needed, reconfigure and change the input pixel format value, the frame rate
 141:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         value, the capture Mode , the destination memory address , the syncunmask values,
 142:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         Multiline value and Limit value using respectively
