 144:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_SetCaptureMode(), HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_SetMemoryAddress(), HAL_DCMIPP_SetSyncUnm
 145:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****         HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_EnableLineEvent() and HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_EnableLimitEvent().
 146:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
 147:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c ****     (#) To read the transferred data counter , use the HAL_DCMIPP_PIPE_GetDataCounter()
 148:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dcmipp.c **** 
